Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.53,0:00:03.00,Narration Off,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}My name's Shin'ichi Kudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.00,0:00:04.53,Narration Off,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Until just recently, I was a famous high school detective
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.53,0:00:06.20,Narration Off,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}known throughout the entire country!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.20,0:00:07.93,Narration Off,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But a mysterious organization forced me to take a pill,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.93,0:00:09.37,Narration Off,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}turning me into Conan Edogawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.37,0:00:10.47,Narration Off,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Doesn't matter if I'm small!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.47,0:00:11.90,Narration Off,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}My mind is that of a former great detective,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.90,0:00:13.27,Narration Off,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and no matter what sort of incident takes place,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.27,0:00:15.50,Narration Off,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}- there is always only one truth!\N- there is always only one truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.51,0:01:59.28,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You know Shin'ichi Kudo, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-oneechan{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.28,0:02:01.48,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Well, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.48,0:02:02.85,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:06.75,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you know the super-famous high school detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.75,0:02:09.85,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He wouldn't happen to be your boyfriend, would he?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.85,0:02:12.69,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,- No! Nothing of the sort!\N- No! Nothing of the sort!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.02,0:02:15.86,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you reacting the same way?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.86,0:02:17.76,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's just thatâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.76,0:02:19.63,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He's your boyfriend, isn't he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.63,0:02:22.90,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.90,0:02:25.89,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't really answer that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.70,0:02:30.04,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're home!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.81,0:02:35.01,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, what could Shin'ichi be doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.01,0:02:37.48,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while since I last heard anything from him...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.48,0:02:41.58,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The case he's working on has probably hit a hard spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.58,0:02:46.09,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But normally he solves all of his cases\Nwithout any problems at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.09,0:02:48.92,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think that maybe he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.92,0:02:50.92,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...gotten worse at being a detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.06,0:02:56.40,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.87,0:03:02.36,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.94,0:03:07.93,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry, little boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.88,0:03:13.35,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.35,0:03:14.68,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.72,0:03:19.22,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Ogawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.22,0:03:21.32,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Since about 2 years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.32,0:03:25.16,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,someone has been sending me toys and money every month.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.16,0:03:26.63,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of creepy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.63,0:03:30.90,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,because the sender's name and address are always made-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.90,0:03:32.44,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Toys and money, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:35.30,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any children?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.30,0:03:39.00,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. A 5-year old son named Yuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.58,0:03:43.18,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly how much money have they been sending?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.18,0:03:44.88,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,1 million yen each month.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.88,0:03:47.18,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It will total 25 million this month!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.18,0:03:49.48,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,- 25 million?!\N- 25 million?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.69,0:03:54.86,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta loves the fact that new toys come every month,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.86,0:03:58.56,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,but being sent money is too creepy for me so I haven't touched any of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.56,0:04:01.50,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, I wouldn't mind holding on to the money for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.50,0:04:02.50,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.50,0:04:05.03,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I was just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.03,0:04:08.07,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any ideas who it could be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.07,0:04:09.31,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.31,0:04:12.51,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure it isn't one of your patients?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.51,0:04:13.94,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Patients?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.94,0:04:17.18,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're a surgeon, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.18,0:04:18.41,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.41,0:04:20.85,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then it wouldn't be strange for one of the patients you saved
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.85,0:04:23.25,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,to send all this to you in appreciation for your help, would it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.25,0:04:24.91,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.99,0:04:30.62,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I don't remember mentioning that I was a surgeon...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.96,0:04:34.83,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know that, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.83,0:04:37.13,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It was his index fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:38.33,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My fingers?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.33,0:04:41.44,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You have diagonal marks on your fingers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.44,0:04:42.61,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,When performing operations,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.61,0:04:48.38,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,surgeons use both index fingers to sew tight sutures.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.38,0:04:52.18,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Over time, it causes diagonal marks to appear on their index fingers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:54.45,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is he right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.45,0:04:55.42,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.42,0:04:58.42,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, I performed a surgery just this very morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.42,0:05:00.75,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent work, my lad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.16,0:05:05.19,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This kid knows all sorts of weird stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.19,0:05:07.16,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But that was amazing, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.16,0:05:09.40,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That was almost likeâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.40,0:05:11.40,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Almost like...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.40,0:05:14.20,Flashback,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}You're in a gymnastics club, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.20,0:05:19.78,Flashback,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Only people who train on the horizontal bar ever get this many blisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.78,0:05:22.28,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Almost like Shin'ichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.28,0:05:24.61,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}H-He couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.38,0:05:29.94,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He couldn't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.95,0:05:33.62,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This came today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.46,0:05:40.13,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There doesn't seem to be anything strange besides the money...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.13,0:05:45.43,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No! Normally it's a much larger package with both toys and money in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.43,0:05:47.93,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time it's been like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.27,0:05:50.76,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.55,0:05:56.52,Dialogue Top,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"I have finished paying the 25 million yen.\NI will be coming to get what is mine."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.05,0:05:59.25,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.25,0:06:01.91,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your guess is as good as mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.02,0:06:12.29,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why don't these have those line patterns on them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.29,0:06:14.10,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Line patterns?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:16.70,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's one on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.70,0:06:19.30,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you mean a barcode.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.30,0:06:21.04,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That is strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.04,0:06:23.30,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't any on any of these things!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.31,0:06:27.31,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They don't sell these toys in stores anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.31,0:06:30.05,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And it looks like some have been damaged...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.05,0:06:32.11,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, ever since the toys started coming in,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.11,0:06:35.52,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,some of them were worn out, and others were completely broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.52,0:06:38.19,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, they've either been sending used toys
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.19,0:06:41.29,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,or toys that they had purchased quite a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.29,0:06:43.16,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Along with the large sums of money!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.16,0:06:45.76,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.76,0:06:48.13,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:50.50,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...it's just an ordinary prank!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.50,0:06:52.90,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A prank?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.90,0:06:54.84,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.84,0:06:59.01,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}No, it's too complicated for a simple prank.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.01,0:07:02.08,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}And sending all that money for no reason would be pointless...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.08,0:07:04.15,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}And then there's that letter...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.15,0:07:07.42,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You have such excellent powers of deduction, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.42,0:07:09.41,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That was nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.02,0:07:15.82,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}No! Dad didn't figure any of those things out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.82,0:07:19.30,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It was all because of Conan{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-kun{\r\be10}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.30,0:07:21.73,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.73,0:07:23.87,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He couldn't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.73,0:07:27.94,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So this letter is the only clue as to who the sender is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.94,0:07:31.17,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Say, do you think the sender could be trying to buy something
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.17,0:07:33.18,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,from Ogawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:36.85,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Depending on how you interpret it,\Nit could mean something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.85,0:07:38.45,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.45,0:07:41.75,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There is a painting in the hospital that my grandfather left me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.75,0:07:45.29,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure they said that it was worth about 20 million yen...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.29,0:07:46.76,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.76,0:07:50.59,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The sender must want to buy that painting from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.59,0:07:53.80,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all go to the hospital\Nand have a look at the painting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.80,0:07:55.86,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We may find more details!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.86,0:07:57.80,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,OK! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.76,0:08:00.73,Dialogue Top,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"Beika Hospital"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.77,0:08:03.61,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This certainly is a large hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.61,0:08:07.58,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I, too, was surprised when\NI first came here 3 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.58,0:08:11.31,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I was transferred here from a small, rural hospital, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.31,0:08:14.12,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ogawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}. Another one of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.12,0:08:16.19,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Another one this year, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.19,0:08:19.39,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Morning glories? With the weather as cold as it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.39,0:08:23.36,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can only assume that the person has been growing them in a greenhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.36,0:08:25.53,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, they've been sending these too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.53,0:08:28.23,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the same person has been sending these as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.23,0:08:30.77,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But the flowers only come once a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.77,0:08:33.57,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,On today, February 19th.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:37.14,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sending flowers must mean the sender is female...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.14,0:08:41.51,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The phrase associated with morning glories is "a short-lived love".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.51,0:08:45.28,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you did something with another woman 2 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.28,0:08:47.58,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing of the sort!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.58,0:08:50.29,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then could it be your son's birthday or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.29,0:08:53.12,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta's birthday is in December.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.12,0:08:55.39,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If it's OK with him,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.39,0:08:58.43,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,why don't we have a look at Ogawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}'s medical records?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:09:02.16,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There might be a patient who has something to do with February 19th!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.16,0:09:03.53,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.53,0:09:05.90,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,May we have a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.90,0:09:08.37,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not allowed to show the records to other people...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.37,0:09:10.34,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Can't we bend the rules just this once?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.34,0:09:13.94,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. I suppose I have no other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.94,0:09:15.93,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to bother you like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.28,0:09:27.55,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, here are all of my patients' records for the past 3 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.16,0:09:34.73,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And there's nobody in here who might want that painting?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.73,0:09:35.80,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.80,0:09:38.13,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Say, would you like to see the painting for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.13,0:09:40.24,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.24,0:09:43.94,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's hanging in the patients' waiting room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.94,0:09:45.94,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're not coming, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.94,0:09:48.04,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wait here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.04,0:09:51.48,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,OK. Then be a good boy and behave yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:53.12,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.12,0:09:56.78,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The painting is quite popular among many of the patients too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.13,0:10:11.73,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Conan{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-kun{\r\be10}! Something's not right!{re-divide}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.73,0:10:14.47,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He's acting too strangely for an ordinary grade school student!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.47,0:10:17.47,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Yeah! Back then, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.47,0:10:21.44,Flashback,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}So this dog barks at all strangers then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.44,0:10:22.91,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}And that other time too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.91,0:10:27.65,Flashback,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}How did you know this was a lighter if you've never been here before?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.65,0:10:31.25,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It was almost like Shin'ichi was giving suggestions!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:33.12,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.12,0:10:36.25,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The day Shin'ichi disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.26,0:10:40.16,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}...Conan{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-kun{\r\be10} showed up, in his place, almost...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:47.66,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Could he actually be Shin'ichi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.91,0:10:54.64,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I'll have to make sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.64,0:10:56.01,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.88,0:11:00.98,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.98,0:11:04.25,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be reading people's records without permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.25,0:11:06.52,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,R-Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.52,0:11:08.16,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.16,0:11:09.93,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sort of.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.93,0:11:14.70,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He said earlier that the flowers are sent to the hospital once a year, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.70,0:11:19.80,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That makes me think that it was a former patient here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.80,0:11:23.71,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It was 2 years ago when he started receiving the toys and the money,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.71,0:11:25.71,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,so that narrows it down to patients who were here
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.71,0:11:28.21,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,during Ogawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s first year at this hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.21,0:11:29.75,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Among them, there are 8 people
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:32.25,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,who have something to do with February 19th.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.25,0:11:34.75,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,People whose surgeries were successful on that day,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.75,0:11:37.25,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,or people who were released or checked in on that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.25,0:11:42.59,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sending flowers most likely means the person is grateful to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:44.79,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,but they bother me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.79,0:11:48.46,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The morning glories grown with care in a greenhouse, and that letter...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:53.97,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing that you could figure that much out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.97,0:11:58.34,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Great work, Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.34,0:12:00.00,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It was nothingâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.17,0:12:11.90,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.90,0:12:14.01,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You are Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.01,0:12:16.44,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you talking about, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.44,0:12:20.15,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Conan! Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.15,0:12:22.27,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Stop playing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.35,0:12:27.25,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Not good! She's found me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.25,0:12:29.89,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}If word gets out that I'm actually Shin'ichi Kudo,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.89,0:12:32.49,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}they'll come back to kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.49,0:12:33.73,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}And if that happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.73,0:12:36.40,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}they might go after Ran and the others as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.40,0:12:38.39,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I have to fool her somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.80,0:12:43.73,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! A Game Man! And Yaiba's Great Adventure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.87,0:12:48.61,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Go Yaiba! Beat up Onimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.61,0:12:50.71,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.71,0:12:54.11,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I think he's faking! It's too suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.11,0:12:56.62,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Conan{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-kun{\r\be10} must really be Shin'ichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.62,0:12:58.35,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But this sort of thing doesn't happen;
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.35,0:13:00.95,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}this isn't a science fiction movie, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.95,0:13:02.35,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.35,0:13:04.99,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}If he really is, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.99,0:13:06.63,Flashback,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Say, Conan{\rHonorifics - Flashback\be10}-kun{\r\be10}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.63,0:13:08.36,Flashback,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Is there anyone you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.36,0:13:11.43,Flashback,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I have someone I really like!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.43,0:13:16.13,Flashback,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Don't tell me it's that Shin'ichi boy you were looking for earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.47,0:13:18.80,Flashback,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.37,0:13:23.14,Flashback,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He's always been kind of a tease since he was a kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.14,0:13:26.41,Flashback,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and he's always been so full of himself and a big mystery geek,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.41,0:13:31.08,Flashback,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}but he's also courageous, cool, and dependable!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.08,0:13:33.61,Flashback,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I really like Shin'ichi a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:40.13,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! Game over!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.13,0:13:42.93,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you wanna try, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.93,0:13:44.86,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You like this sort of thing, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.86,0:13:46.90,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,L-Like...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.90,0:13:50.67,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I do not! Don't get the wrong idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.67,0:13:54.00,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You don't? I'll keep playing then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.51,0:13:57.31,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Tomoya Ogino?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.31,0:14:01.58,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Huh? Ogawa{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} said his son was named Yuta...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.58,0:14:05.45,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Normally you enter your own name\Nor the name of a character you like...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.45,0:14:07.69,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Wait. Tomoya Ogino.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.69,0:14:10.69,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Where have I seen this name before?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.69,0:14:12.02,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.33,0:14:15.83,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.83,0:14:17.36,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Tomoya Ogino, 5 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.36,0:14:19.70,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He died after Ogawa{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} operated on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.70,0:14:21.97,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Three years ago, on February 19th!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.82,0:14:26.82,Dialogue Top,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"I have finished paying the 25 million yen.\NI will be coming to get what is mine."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.44,0:14:30.38,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The letter couldn't mean what I think it does!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.38,0:14:34.71,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ran! Bring Mr. Ogawa here right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.71,0:14:37.15,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! There's no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.08,0:14:40.19,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It has to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:42.72,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That tone, his mannerisms, his deductions...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.72,0:14:46.02,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}They're all exactly like Shin'ichi's!\NNo question about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.02,0:14:49.50,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really find out who the sender is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.50,0:14:53.43,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I think it might be the parents of\NTomoya Ogino{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.43,0:14:56.03,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Tomoya Ogino?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.03,0:14:58.97,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The one who died of appendicitis three years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.97,0:15:01.91,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,People can die from appendicitis?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.91,0:15:05.61,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. If it's not detected early enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.61,0:15:09.72,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It was already too late for him when they brought him in to the hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.72,0:15:13.62,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The boy's father absolutely would not listen to me, however...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.62,0:15:19.69,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But why would he send you presents if the operation wasn't successful?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.69,0:15:22.56,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They're neither presents nor used goods!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.56,0:15:25.83,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They're the belongings of the late\NTomoya Ogino, who died 3 years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.04,0:15:35.01,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, he's been sending\Nall of his son's keepsakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.01,0:15:37.51,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sending them out of hatred!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.51,0:15:40.15,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The flowers are delivered to the hospital every February 19th
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.15,0:15:42.71,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,because it's the anniversary of his son's death!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.71,0:15:46.65,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And that letter means that he's going\Nto take the life of Ogawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s son
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.65,0:15:48.09,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,on the exact same day!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:49.72,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.72,0:15:51.86,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Where's your son right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.86,0:15:54.96,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My wife should be on her way\Nto pick him up at school!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.96,0:15:56.66,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Contact her at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.40,0:16:00.17,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Someone already picked him up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.17,0:16:02.97,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They told me his father had\Nalready picked him up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.97,0:16:05.37,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.37,0:16:07.41,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,T-This can't be happening...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.41,0:16:08.41,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.41,0:16:11.34,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}If we don't find them soon, Yuta{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-kun{\r\be10}'s a goner!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.34,0:16:13.15,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the school?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.15,0:16:15.45,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't very far from here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.45,0:16:17.95,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then they're still nearby!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.95,0:16:19.28,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.06,0:16:26.53,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Look, little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.53,0:16:28.03,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I have a present for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.03,0:16:29.36,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.36,0:16:31.35,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.10,0:16:37.04,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you really gonna take me to a fun place after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.04,0:16:40.44,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. I'll take you there soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.44,0:16:42.60,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,To where Tomoya is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.88,0:16:46.87,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Where?! Where are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.25,0:16:51.68,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Tomoya!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.68,0:16:53.75,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It must have been lonely all by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.75,0:16:56.92,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I'll bring you a friend soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.92,0:16:58.91,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Right now, in fact!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.60,0:17:06.10,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's Yuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.10,0:17:07.43,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.40,0:17:10.89,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.91,0:17:15.90,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Here goes! Try this on for size!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.02,0:17:27.75,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.54,0:17:50.44,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Did Conan{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-kun{\r\be10} do that just now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.44,0:17:52.14,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.15,0:17:54.71,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.71,0:17:56.44,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.38,0:18:00.92,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.92,0:18:03.72,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Move and you know what'll happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.72,0:18:06.46,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ogino{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}! So it was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.46,0:18:08.39,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! It was me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.39,0:18:11.20,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the father of Tomoya Ogino,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:13.37,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,who you killed 3 years ago when you messed up his operation!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.37,0:18:15.60,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.60,0:18:17.40,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It was already too late when they carried himâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:20.41,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! As if you would understand\Nthe feelings of a father
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:23.38,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,whose son was murdered just after he turned 5!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.38,0:18:28.48,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All I had left were his remains and the 25 million in insurance money!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.48,0:18:31.05,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why you sent all that money...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.05,0:18:32.35,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.35,0:18:36.12,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The money, his toys, and the morning glories that he loved so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.12,0:18:38.79,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It was with my hatred that I sent them all to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.79,0:18:43.10,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's your turn to feel what it's like to lose your own son!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.10,0:18:47.03,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Don't hurt my son!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.03,0:18:49.47,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kill me instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.47,0:18:53.17,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just let my son go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.17,0:18:58.04,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! So you were the one who sent the toys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.04,0:18:59.64,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.64,0:19:03.08,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I always take good care of them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.08,0:19:05.07,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,T-Tomoya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:14.96,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Tomoya...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.96,0:19:16.26,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.26,0:19:19.26,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Did Daddy and the others say something bad to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.26,0:19:21.40,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.40,0:19:24.00,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I was the bad one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.00,0:19:25.60,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.60,0:19:28.97,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I knew from the very start that it wasn't his fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.97,0:19:34.78,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But I had to fool myself into thinking it was, or else I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.21,0:19:39.55,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, little boy! I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.82,0:19:43.31,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ran. Call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.86,0:19:47.56,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Please don't get the police involved!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.56,0:19:51.06,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But he just tried to kill your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.06,0:19:52.93,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.93,0:19:55.16,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.17,0:20:00.94,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ogino{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}. I know exactly how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.94,0:20:05.27,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I am a father before I'm a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.91,0:20:10.48,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How lucky it was that it didn't turn into a serious incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.48,0:20:14.55,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But why did he send the money and toys for 2 whole years?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.55,0:20:18.12,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He was probably waiting for Yuta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} to turn 5 first.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.12,0:20:21.76,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The same age that Tomoya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} was when he died 3 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.76,0:20:24.20,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:26.53,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent deduction skills you have there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.93,0:20:32.27,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm just a kid so I don't really know for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.27,0:20:33.97,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I just remembered something I have to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.97,0:20:35.46,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Go on home without me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.04,0:20:39.81,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.95,0:22:16.09,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.09,0:22:18.23,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.23,0:22:21.23,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He went drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.23,0:22:24.90,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You must be hungry. I'll make you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.90,0:22:25.97,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.97,0:22:27.17,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.17,0:22:30.36,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I hear our shop teacher Kishida{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} is getting married!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.37,0:22:33.20,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That gorilla?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.41,0:22:40.58,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know about my high school teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.58,0:22:43.98,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, uh, you're always talking\Nabout how he's a gorilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.98,0:22:45.32,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.32,0:22:49.79,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't believe it at first,\Nbut I guess you really are Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.79,0:22:51.59,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'mâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.59,0:22:54.93,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just confess already! Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.17,0:23:00.60,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,T-The phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.60,0:23:01.80,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let it ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.80,0:23:04.67,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.67,0:23:07.11,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! I'll pick it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.41,0:23:13.05,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, this is the Mouri Detectiveâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.05,0:23:14.48,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Hey, Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.48,0:23:15.85,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It's been a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.85,0:23:18.12,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,S-Shin'ichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.12,0:23:20.15,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No way! You're right hâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.15,0:23:24.16,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now. Have you already forgotten the sound of my voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.16,0:23:26.56,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.56,0:23:29.73,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Darn that Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.73,0:23:32.90,Flashback,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Please, Dr. Agasa! I think Ran's on to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.90,0:23:35.97,Flashback,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Call her using my voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.97,0:23:39.24,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He shouldn't have made her worry so much like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.24,0:23:40.71,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.71,0:23:43.71,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you there, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.71,0:23:47.71,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so stupid! I think I misunderstood things!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.71,0:23:49.78,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.78,0:23:53.35,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Shin'ichi. Have you started using words that old men use?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.35,0:23:54.84,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Have I?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.19,0:23:59.18,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're a life-saver.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.60,0:24:07.40,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT EPISODE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.60,0:24:07.40,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,60 seconds until the next episode's hint!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.20,0:24:05.70,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many beautiful paintings!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.70,0:24:07.23,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad we came!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.23,0:24:09.40,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this! The colors are lovely!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.21,0:24:22.05,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that expression?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.48,0:24:25.42,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's on the card that he's so shocked about?!
